cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about generating optical flow ground truths for training deep networks. The most relevant sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with image and video analysis. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also likely sub-categories as the paper discusses training deep networks. Robotics (cs.RO) is another possible sub-category as optical flow is used in robot navigation. Multimedia (cs.MM) is also a possible sub-category as it deals with video analysis.
